text: Suwa Taisha is a Shinto shrine in Nagano Prefecture. It is the ichinomiya or highest ranked shrine of the former Shinano Province and is very old. ==References== Category:Kanpei-taisha Category:Suwa cult Category:Suwa shrines Category:Beppyo shrines Category:My≈çjin Taisha Category:Taisha Category:Shinto shrines in Nagano Prefecture
